When searching using &quot;Tools &gt; Find Messages (S)&quot; no messages can be found. The result list will remain empty and the window will state &quot;0 matches&quot;.

Reproducible: Always

Steps to Reproduce:
1.Use Tools &gt; Find Messages
2.Choose a folder, and something to search
3.Click &apos;Search&apos;
Actual Results:  
0 matches

Expected Results:  
A list of mails that contain the words being searched

I received the suggestion that duplicate messages could cause this behaviour, but there were none.
Bug https://bugs.kde.org/show_bug.cgi?id=353671 might be related, but the workaround (erasing the Search folder and restarting Kmail) does not work.</thetext>
